var book = {
	"name": "1 John",
	"numChapters": 5,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30525A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30525A\"></sup>That which was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30525B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30525B\"></sup>from the beginning, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30525C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30525C\"></sup>which we have heard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30525D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30525D\"></sup>which we have seen with our eyes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30525E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30525E\"></sup>which we looked upon and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30525F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30525F\"></sup>have touched with our hands, concerning the word of life—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30526G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30526G\"></sup>the life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30526H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30526H\"></sup>was made manifest, and we have seen it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30526I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30526I\"></sup>testify to it and proclaim to you the eternal life, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30526J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30526J\"></sup>which was with the Father and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30526K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30526K\"></sup>was made manifest to us—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30527L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30527L\"></sup>that which we have seen and heard we proclaim also to you, so that you too may have fellowship with us; and indeed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30527M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30527M\"></sup>our fellowship is with the Father and with his Son Jesus Christ.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And we are writing these things so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30528N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30528N\"></sup>that our joy may be complete.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30529O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30529O\"></sup>This is the message we have heard from him and proclaim to you, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30529P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30529P\"></sup>God is light, and in him is no darkness at all.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30530Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30530Q\"></sup>If we say we have fellowship with him while we walk in darkness, we lie and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30530R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30530R\"></sup>do not practice the truth.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30531S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30531S\"></sup>if we walk in the light, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30531T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30531T\"></sup>as he is in the light, we have fellowship with one another, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30531U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30531U\"></sup>the blood of Jesus his Son cleanses us from all sin.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30532V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30532V\"></sup>If we say we have no sin, we deceive ourselves, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30532W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30532W\"></sup>the truth is not in us.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30533X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30533X\"></sup>If we confess our sins, he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30533Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30533Y\"></sup>faithful and just to forgive us our sins and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30533Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30533Z\"></sup>to cleanse us from all unrighteousness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>If we say we have not sinned, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30534AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30534AA\"></sup>we make him a liar, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30534AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30534AB\"></sup>his word is not in us."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>My little children, I am writing these things to you so that you may not sin. But if anyone does sin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30535A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30535A\"></sup>we have an advocate with the Father, Jesus Christ the righteous.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30536B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30536B\"></sup>He is the propitiation for our sins, and not for ours only but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30536C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30536C\"></sup>also for the sins of the whole world.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And by this we know that we have come to know him, if we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30537D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30537D\"></sup>keep his commandments.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Whoever says “I know him” but does not keep his commandments <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30538E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30538E\"></sup>is a liar, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30538F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30538F\"></sup>the truth is not in him,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>but whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30539G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30539G\"></sup>keeps his word, in him truly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30539H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30539H\"></sup>the love of God is perfected. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30539I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30539I\"></sup>By this we may know that we are in him:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>whoever says he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30540J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30540J\"></sup>abides in him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30540K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30540K\"></sup>ought to walk in the same way in which he walked.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Beloved, I am writing you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30541L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30541L\"></sup>no new commandment, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30541M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30541M\"></sup>an old commandment <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30541N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30541N\"></sup>that you had from the beginning. The old commandment is the word that you have heard.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>At the same time, it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30542O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30542O\"></sup>a new commandment that I am writing to you, which is true in him and in you, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30542P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30542P\"></sup>the darkness is passing away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30542Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30542Q\"></sup>the true light is already shining.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Whoever says he is in the light and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30543R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30543R\"></sup>hates his brother is still in darkness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Whoever loves his brother abides in the light, and in him there is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30544S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30544S\"></sup>cause for stumbling.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But whoever hates his brother is in the darkness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30545T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30545T\"></sup>walks in the darkness, and does not know where he is going, because the darkness has blinded his eyes.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I am writing to you, little children,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30546U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30546U\"></sup>your sins are forgiven for his name's sake.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I am writing to you, fathers,because you know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30547V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30547V\"></sup>him who is from the beginning.I am writing to you, young men,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30547W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30547W\"></sup>you have overcome the evil one.I write to you, children,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30547X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30547X\"></sup>you know the Father.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I write to you, fathers,because you know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30548Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30548Y\"></sup>him who is from the beginning.I write to you, young men,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30548Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30548Z\"></sup>you are strong,and the word of God abides in you,and you have overcome the evil one.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30549AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30549AA\"></sup>Do not love the world or the things in the world. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30549AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30549AB\"></sup>If anyone loves the world, the love of the Father is not in him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For all that is in the world—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30550AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30550AC\"></sup>the desires of the flesh and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30550AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30550AD\"></sup>the desires of the eyes and pride of life—is not from the Father but is from the world.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30551AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30551AE\"></sup>the world is passing away along with its desires, but whoever does the will of God abides forever.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30552AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30552AF\"></sup>it is the last hour, and as you have heard that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30552AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30552AG\"></sup>antichrist is coming, so now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30552AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30552AH\"></sup>many antichrists have come. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30552AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30552AI\"></sup>Therefore we know that it is the last hour.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30553AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30553AJ\"></sup>They went out from us, but they were not of us; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30553AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30553AK\"></sup>if they had been of us, they would have continued with us. But they went out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30553AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30553AL\"></sup>that it might become plain that they all are not of us.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But you have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30554AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30554AM\"></sup>anointed by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30554AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30554AN\"></sup>the Holy One, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30554AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30554AO\"></sup>you all have knowledge.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I write to you, not because you do not know the truth, but because you know it, and because no lie is of the truth.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Who is the liar but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30556AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30556AP\"></sup>he who denies that Jesus is the Christ? This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30556AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30556AQ\"></sup>the antichrist, he who denies the Father and the Son.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30557AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30557AR\"></sup>No one who denies the Son has the Father. Whoever confesses the Son has the Father also.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30558AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30558AS\"></sup>what you heard from the beginning abide in you. If what you heard from the beginning abides in you, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30558AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30558AT\"></sup>you too will abide in the Son and in the Father.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And this is the promise that he made to us—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30559AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30559AU\"></sup>eternal life.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I write these things to you about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30560AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30560AV\"></sup>those who are trying to deceive you.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30561AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30561AW\"></sup>the anointing that you received from him abides in you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30561AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30561AX\"></sup>you have no need that anyone should teach you. But as his anointing teaches you about everything, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30561AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30561AY\"></sup>is true, and is no lie—just as it has taught you, abide in him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And now, little children, abide in him, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30562AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30562AZ\"></sup>when he appears <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30562BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30562BA\"></sup>we may have confidence and not shrink from him in shame at his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30562BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30562BB\"></sup>coming.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>If you know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30563BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30563BC\"></sup>he is righteous, you may be sure that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30563BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30563BD\"></sup>everyone who practices righteousness has been born of him."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>See <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30564A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30564A\"></sup>what kind of love the Father has given to us, that we should be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30564B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30564B\"></sup>children of God; and so we are. The reason why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30564C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30564C\"></sup>the world does not know us is that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30564D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30564D\"></sup>it did not know him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Beloved, we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30565E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30565E\"></sup>God's children <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30565F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30565F\"></sup>now, and what we will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30565G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30565G\"></sup>has not yet appeared; but we know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30565H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30565H\"></sup>when he appears <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30565I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30565I\"></sup>we shall be like him, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30565J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30565J\"></sup>we shall see him as he is.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30566K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30566K\"></sup>thus hopes in him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30566L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30566L\"></sup>purifies himself as he is pure.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Everyone who makes a practice of sinning also practices lawlessness; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30567M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30567M\"></sup>sin is lawlessness.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30568N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30568N\"></sup>he appeared in order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30568O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30568O\"></sup>take away sins, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30568P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30568P\"></sup>in him there is no sin.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>No one who abides in him keeps on sinning; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30569Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30569Q\"></sup>no one who keeps on sinning has either seen him or known him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Little children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30570R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30570R\"></sup>let no one deceive you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30570S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30570S\"></sup>Whoever practices righteousness is righteous, as he is righteous.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30571T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30571T\"></sup>Whoever makes a practice of sinning is of the devil, for the devil has been sinning from the beginning. The reason the Son of God appeared was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30571U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30571U\"></sup>to destroy the works of the devil.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30572V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30572V\"></sup>No one born of God makes a practice of sinning, for God's seed abides in him; and he cannot keep on sinning, because he has been born of God.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>By this it is evident who are the children of God, and who are the children of the devil: whoever does not practice righteousness is not of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30573W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30573W\"></sup>nor is the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30573X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30573X\"></sup>does not love his brother.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30574Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30574Y\"></sup>this is the message that you have heard from the beginning, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30574Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30574Z\"></sup>that we should love one another.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>We should not be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30575AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30575AA\"></sup>Cain, who was of the evil one and murdered his brother. And why did he murder him? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30575AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30575AB\"></sup>Because his own deeds were evil and his brother's righteous.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do not be surprised, brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30576AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30576AC\"></sup>that the world hates you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>We know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30577AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30577AD\"></sup>we have passed out of death into life, because we love the brothers. Whoever does not love abides in death.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30578AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30578AE\"></sup>Everyone who hates his brother is a murderer, and you know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30578AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30578AF\"></sup>no murderer has eternal life abiding in him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>By this we know love, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30579AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30579AG\"></sup>he laid down his life for us, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30579AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30579AH\"></sup>we ought to lay down our lives for the brothers.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30580AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30580AI\"></sup>if anyone has the world's goods and sees his brother in need, yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30580AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30580AJ\"></sup>closes his heart against him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30580AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30580AK\"></sup>how does God's love abide in him?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Little children, let us not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30581AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30581AL\"></sup>love in word or talk but in deed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30581AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30581AM\"></sup>in truth.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>By this we shall know that we are of the truth and reassure our heart before him;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>for whenever our heart condemns us, God is greater than our heart, and he knows everything.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Beloved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30584AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30584AN\"></sup>if our heart does not condemn us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30584AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30584AO\"></sup>we have confidence before God;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30585AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30585AP\"></sup>whatever we ask we receive from him, because we keep his commandments and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30585AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30585AQ\"></sup>do what pleases him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And this is his commandment, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30586AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30586AR\"></sup>that we believe in the name of his Son Jesus Christ and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30586AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30586AS\"></sup>love one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30586AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30586AT\"></sup>just as he has commanded us.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30587AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30587AU\"></sup>Whoever keeps his commandments abides in God, and God in him. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30587AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30587AV\"></sup>by this we know that he abides in us, by the Spirit whom he has given us."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Beloved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30588A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30588A\"></sup>do not believe every spirit, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30588B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30588B\"></sup>test the spirits to see whether they are from God, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30588C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30588C\"></sup>many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30588D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30588D\"></sup>false prophets <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30588E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30588E\"></sup>have gone out into the world.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>By this you know the Spirit of God: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30589F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30589F\"></sup>every spirit that confesses that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30589G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30589G\"></sup>Jesus Christ has come in the flesh is from God,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and every spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30590H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30590H\"></sup>that does not confess Jesus is not from God. This is the spirit of the antichrist, which you heard was coming and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30590I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30590I\"></sup>now is in the world already.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Little children, you are from God and have overcome them, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30591J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30591J\"></sup>he who is in you is greater than <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30591K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30591K\"></sup>he who is in the world.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30592L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30592L\"></sup>They are from the world; therefore they speak from the world, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30592M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30592M\"></sup>the world listens to them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>We are from God. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30593N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30593N\"></sup>Whoever knows God listens to us; whoever is not from God does not listen to us. By this we know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30593O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30593O\"></sup>the Spirit of truth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30593P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30593P\"></sup>the spirit of error.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Beloved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30594Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30594Q\"></sup>let us love one another, for love is from God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30594R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30594R\"></sup>whoever loves has been born of God and knows God.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30595S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30595S\"></sup>Anyone who does not love does not know God, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30595T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30595T\"></sup>God is love.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In this the love of God was made manifest among us, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30596U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30596U\"></sup>God sent his only Son into the world, so that we might live through him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In this is love, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30597V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30597V\"></sup>not that we have loved God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30597W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30597W\"></sup>but that he loved us and sent his Son to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30597X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30597X\"></sup>the propitiation for our sins.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Beloved, if God so loved us, we also ought to love one another.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30599Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30599Y\"></sup>No one has ever seen God; if we love one another, God abides in us and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30599Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30599Z\"></sup>his love is perfected in us.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30600AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30600AA\"></sup>By this we know that we abide in him and he in us, because he has given us of his Spirit.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30601AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30601AB\"></sup>we have seen and testify that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30601AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30601AC\"></sup>the Father has sent his Son to be the Savior of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30601AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30601AD\"></sup>the world.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30602AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30602AE\"></sup>Whoever confesses that Jesus is the Son of God, God abides in him, and he in God.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30603AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30603AF\"></sup>we have come to know and to believe the love that God has for us. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30603AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30603AG\"></sup>God is love, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30603AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30603AH\"></sup>whoever abides in love abides in God, and God abides in him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>By this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30604AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30604AI\"></sup>is love perfected with us, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30604AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30604AJ\"></sup>we may have confidence for the day of judgment, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30604AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30604AK\"></sup>as he is so also are we in this world.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>There is no fear in love, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30605AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30605AL\"></sup>perfect love casts out fear. For fear has to do with punishment, and whoever fears has not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30605AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30605AM\"></sup>been perfected in love.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30606AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30606AN\"></sup>We love because he first loved us.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30607AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30607AO\"></sup>If anyone says, “I love God,” and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30607AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30607AP\"></sup>hates his brother, he is a liar; for he who does not love his brother whom he has seen cannot love God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30607AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30607AQ\"></sup>whom he has not seen.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30608AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30608AR\"></sup>this commandment we have from him: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30608AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30608AS\"></sup>whoever loves God must also love his brother."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30609A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30609A\"></sup>Everyone who believes that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30609B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30609B\"></sup>Jesus is the Christ has been born of God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30609C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30609C\"></sup>everyone who loves the Father loves whoever has been born of him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30610D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30610D\"></sup>By this we know that we love the children of God, when we love God and obey his commandments.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30611E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30611E\"></sup>this is the love of God, that we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30611F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30611F\"></sup>keep his commandments. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30611G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30611G\"></sup>his commandments are not burdensome.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30612H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30612H\"></sup>everyone who has been born of God overcomes the world. And this is the victory that has overcome the world—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30612I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30612I\"></sup>our faith.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Who is it that overcomes the world except the one who believes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30613J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30613J\"></sup>that Jesus is the Son of God?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This is he who came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30614K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30614K\"></sup>by water and blood—Jesus Christ; not by the water only but by the water and the blood. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30614L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30614L\"></sup>the Spirit is the one who testifies, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30614M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30614M\"></sup>the Spirit is the truth.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For there are three that testify:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>the Spirit and the water and the blood; and these three agree.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30617N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30617N\"></sup>If we receive the testimony of men, the testimony of God is greater, for this is the testimony of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30617O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30617O\"></sup>that he has borne concerning his Son.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Whoever believes in the Son of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30618P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30618P\"></sup>has the testimony in himself. Whoever does not believe God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30618Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30618Q\"></sup>has made him a liar, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30618R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30618R\"></sup>because he has not believed in the testimony that God has borne concerning his Son.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And this is the testimony, that God gave us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30619S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30619S\"></sup>eternal life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30619T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30619T\"></sup>this life is in his Son.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30620U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30620U\"></sup>Whoever has the Son has life; whoever does not have the Son of God does not have life.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I write <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30621V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30621V\"></sup>these things to you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30621W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30621W\"></sup>believe in the name of the Son of God, that you may know that you have eternal life.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And this is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30622X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30622X\"></sup>the confidence that we have toward him, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30622Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30622Y\"></sup>if we ask anything according to his will he hears us.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And if we know that he hears us in whatever we ask, we know that we have the requests that we have asked of him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If anyone sees his brother committing a sin not leading to death, he shall ask, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30624Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30624Z\"></sup>God will give him life—to those who commit sins that do not lead to death. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30624AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30624AA\"></sup>There is sin that leads to death; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30624AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30624AB\"></sup>I do not say that one should pray for that.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30625AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30625AC\"></sup>All wrongdoing is sin, but there is sin that does not lead to death.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>We know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30626AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30626AD\"></sup>everyone who has been born of God does not keep on sinning, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30626AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30626AE\"></sup>he who was born of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30626AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30626AF\"></sup>protects him, and the evil one does not touch him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>We know that we are from God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30627AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30627AG\"></sup>the whole world lies in the power of the evil one.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And we know that the Son of God has come and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30628AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30628AH\"></sup>has given us understanding, so that we may know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30628AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30628AI\"></sup>him who is true; and we are in him who is true, in his Son Jesus Christ. He is the true God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30628AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30628AJ\"></sup>eternal life.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Little children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30629AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30629AK\"></sup>keep yourselves from idols."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;